Description: CDPAP is a Medicaid program that allows consumers to direct their own home care. Visit cdpapny.org/ to learn more about CDPAP.
Headquarters Regions: Greater New York Area, East Coast, Northeastern US
Full Description: What is the Consumer Directed Personal Assistance Program (CDPAP)? The Consumer Directed Personal Assistance Program (CDPAP) is a Medicaid program that allows consumers that need long-term home care to direct their own care. Consumers, or their representatives, recruit their own personal assistants who they train and direct. Who is eligible to join CDPAP? Consumers must require assistance with activities of daily living or skilled care, have a stable medical condition, and be self directing or have a designated representative that is willing and able to direct care as per the program’s requirements. Since CDPAP is a Medicaid sponsored program, it is only available to consumers that are eligible for Medicaid. Who can provide care under CDPAP? May family members serve as the personal assistant? Most people, including children, can serve as personal assistants and get paid to provide care under CDPAP. Spouses may not provide care under CDPAP. http://www.edisonhhc.com/cdpap/

Full Description: ScoreDoc is an online reputation scorecard platform that assesses the online reputation of healthcare providers such as doctors, dentists, chiropractors, private practices, and hospitals.  Most of you use online reviews as part of your doctor selection process. Unfortunately, doctor reviews are scattered all over the internet, and visiting a few review platforms may not give you comprehensive information about their online reputation, resulting in a sub-optimal selection of your healthcare providers. We believe that everyone should have access to the comprehensive reputation scorecard of doctors so that they select the best healthcare providers available to them. ScoreDoc is a key tool for assisting patients in selecting the right healthcare provider. It is an easy-to-use, convenient information source that informs you about the quality of healthcare providers by analyzing online reviews on all major review platforms. Our reputation scorecard platform also employs artificial intelligence to provide medical groups or doctors online reputations, including analysis of sentiment expressed by patient reviews. If you are unsure which healthcare provider to select, enter the details of the physician or practice you are evaluating to generate their comprehensive reputation scorecard. The reputation scorecard will provide you with a percentile score to compare the prospective healthcare provider or practice with other providers in that specialty.
